{"_path":"/maps/_ai/foundations/architectures","_dir":"foundations","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"AI Architectures","description":"System architectures and design patterns for AI systems","original_path":"_ai/architectures.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"模型架构-model-architectures"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模型架构 (Model Architectures)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"litgptpytorch-lightning-原生的-llm-工具包"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LitGPT：PyTorch Lightning 原生的 LLM 工具包"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LitGPT 让在个人数据上训练、微调和部署大模型变得简单高效。它内置 20+ 主流开源架构（Llama、Mistral、Qwen 等），并预配置 Flash Attention、FSDP 分布式训练、4-bit/8-bit 量化等生产级优化，开箱即用。核心代码采用\"单文件模型\"设计，没有过度抽象，适合快速原型验证和学习 LLM 工程实践。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/Lightning-AI/litgpt","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LitGPT GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://lightning.ai/litgpt","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LitGPT 文档"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"mamba线性复杂度的状态空间模型"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mamba：线性复杂度的状态空间模型"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mamba 代表了后 Transformer 时代的重要探索。传统 Transformer 的自注意力机制是二次复杂度 O(n²)，长序列时计算和内存开销爆炸。Mamba 通过选择性状态空间（Selective State Space）将复杂度降至线性 O(n)，同时保留了长程依赖建模能力。2024 年起，Mamba 与 Transformer 的混合架构成为主流——用 Mamba 处理长程上下文，用注意力机制处理局部精细交互。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.00752","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mamba: Linear-Time Sequence Modeling"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://newsletter.maartengrootendorst.com/p/a-visual-guide-to-mamba-and-state","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A Visual Guide to Mamba"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"nanogpt极简-gpt-教学实现"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NanoGPT：极简 GPT 教学实现"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Andrej Karpathy 开发的 NanoGPT 用最简洁的代码实现了完整的 GPT 训练流程，核心代码仅约 300 行。这种\"minimal but complete\"的设计理念，让研究者能聚焦核心机制而非工程细节。配合《Let's build GPT: from scratch》视频系列，是理解 GPT 原理的最佳入门资料。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/karpathy/nanoGPT","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"nanoGPT GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/karpathy/build-nanogpt","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"build-nanogpt 教学仓库"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"rwkvrnn-与-transformer-的混合架构"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RWKV：RNN 与 Transformer 的混合架构"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RWKV（Receptance Weighted Key Value）结合了 RNN 的 O(1) 推理内存和 Transformer 的并行训练能力。训练时像 Transformer 一样并行，推理时像 RNN 一样常数内存——这个特性让它在端侧部署和长文本生成场景有独特优势，支持 10 万+ tokens 的长文本续写。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.13048","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RWKV 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/blog/rwkv","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hugging Face RWKV 介绍"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"torchtitanpytorch-原生大规模训练框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TorchTitan：PyTorch 原生大规模训练框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TorchTitan 是 PyTorch 官方出品的大规模模型训练框架，目标是成为\"PyTorch 原生的 Megatron/DeepSpeed 替代\"。它提供 4D 并行（数据并行、张量并行、流水线并行、序列并行）的统一实现，支持弹性扩缩容。各并行策略可独立开关、自由组合，无需修改模型代码即可无缝应用到大规模训练。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/pytorch/torchtitan","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TorchTitan GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.06511","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TorchTitan 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"jepa非生成式自监督学习架构"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JEPA：非生成式自监督学习架构"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JEPA（Joint Embedding Predictive Architecture）是杨立昆提出的非生成式学习架构，核心创新是在抽象表示空间而非像素/token 空间进行预测。与传统生成模型重建输入不同，JEPA 学习语义表示，一次性预测而无需顺序解码。LeCun 认为这是通向 AGI 的必经之路——真正的智能需要世界模型，而非仅仅自回归生成。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://rohitbandaru.github.io/blog/JEPA-Deep-Dive/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JEPA 深度解析"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ai.meta.com/blog/v-jepa-yann-lecun-ai-model-video-joint-embedding-predictive-architecture/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"V-JEPA 官方发布"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"空间智能理解三维世界的新一代-ai"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"空间智能：理解三维世界的新一代 AI"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李飞飞创立的 World Labs 专注于\"空间智能\"——让 AI 理解三维世界的几何、物理和语义。真正的空间智能世界模型需要三种能力：生成性（创造遵守物理定律的世界）、多模态（融合视觉、语言、空间信息）、交互性（支持探索和导航的 3D 环境）。她预言未来五年，Transformer 可能被淘汰。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.mittrchina.com/news/detail/15468","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李飞飞空间智能长文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1976808836682765387","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"李飞飞万字访谈"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"transformer-基础架构"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer 基础架构"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"transformer-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer 是一种神经网络架构，2017 年在论文 \"Attention is All You Need\" 中首次提出。它已成为深度学习模型的主流架构，驱动着 GPT、Llama、Gemini 等文本生成模型，同时也应用于音频生成、图像识别、蛋白质结构预测等领域。文本生成类 Transformer 的核心原理是"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下一个 token 预测"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——根据用户输入的文本提示，预测最可能的下一个词（或词片段）。其核心创新在于自注意力机制（self-attention），使模型能够处理整个序列并更有效地捕捉长距离依赖关系。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://poloclub.github.io/transformer-explainer/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer Explainer"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"transformer-架构三大组件是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer 架构三大组件是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个文本生成 Transformer 包含三个关键组件："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding（嵌入层）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将文本输入切分为 token（词或子词），转换为捕获语义含义的数值向量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer Block（变换器块）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：模型的核心构建模块，包含：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Attention Mechanism（注意力机制）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：允许 token 之间通信，捕获上下文信息和词间关系"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLP（多层感知机）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：对每个 token 独立操作，精化每个 token 的表示"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Output Probabilities（输出概率）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：最终的线性层和 softmax 层将处理后的嵌入转换为概率，预测序列中的下一个 token"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"embedding-层如何将文本转换为向量表示"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding 层如何将文本转换为向量表示？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding 层将输入提示转换为模型可理解的数值表示，包含四个步骤："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tokenization（分词）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将输入文本切分为 token（词或子词）。GPT-2 的词表有 50,257 个唯一 token"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Token Embedding（词嵌入）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每个 token 被表示为 768 维向量（维度因模型而异）。相似含义的 token 在高维空间中距离更近"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Positional Encoding（位置编码）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：编码每个 token 在输入序列中的位置信息。GPT-2 从零开始训练自己的位置编码矩阵"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Final Embedding（最终嵌入）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将 token 编码和位置编码相加，得到最终的嵌入表示"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"多头自注意力机制如何工作"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多头自注意力机制如何工作？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自注意力机制使模型能够捕获序列中 token 之间的关系："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Q/K/V 矩阵计算"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：每个 token 的嵌入向量被转换为三个向量——Query（查询）、Key（键）、Value（值）。可用搜索类比理解：Q 是搜索框输入，K 是网页标题，V 是网页内容"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多头分割"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Q/K/V 向量被分割成多个头（GPT-2 small 有 12 个头），每个头独立处理嵌入的不同段，捕获不同的句法和语义关系"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Masked Self-Attention（掩码自注意力）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"计算 Q 和 K 的点积得到注意力分数"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对注意力矩阵的上三角应用 mask，防止模型访问未来 token（不能\"偷看\"未来）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"经过 softmax 转换为概率，每行总和为 1"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输出和拼接"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将注意力分数与 V 矩阵相乘，12 个头的输出拼接后通过线性投影"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"mlp-层的作用是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLP 层的作用是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MLP（多层感知机）在自注意力之后增强模型的表示能力："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"包含两个线性变换，中间使用 GELU 激活函数"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一次线性变换将维度从 768 扩展到 3072（4 倍），允许模型在高维空间捕获更复杂的模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二次线性变换将维度压缩回 768，保留有用的非线性变换"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与自注意力不同，MLP 独立处理每个 token，仅将每个 token 的表示从一个空间映射到另一个空间"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"输出概率如何生成下一个-token"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"输出概率如何生成下一个 token？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"经过所有 Transformer Block 处理后："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最终线性层将表示投影到 50,257 维空间（词表大小），每个 token 对应一个 logit 值"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Softmax 将 logits 转换为概率分布（总和为 1）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过采样生成下一个 token，关键超参数：\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Temperature"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：控制随机性\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"=1：无影响"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<1：更确定、更尖锐的分布"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1：更柔和、更\"有创意\"的分布"}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Top-k 采样"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：仅考虑概率最高的 k 个 token"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Top-p 采样"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：考虑累积概率超过阈值 p 的最小 token 集合"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"辅助架构特性有哪些"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辅助架构特性有哪些？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Layer Normalization（层归一化）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：稳定训练、加速收敛，在每个 Transformer Block 中应用两次（注意力前和 MLP 前）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dropout（随机失活）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：训练时随机将部分权重设为零，防止过拟合；推理时关闭"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Residual Connections（残差连接）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：绕过一层或多层的快捷连接，缓解梯度消失问题，使深层网络训练成为可能。GPT-2 在每个 Transformer Block 中使用两次"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"litgptpytorch-lightning-原生的-llm-工具包","depth":2,"text":"LitGPT：PyTorch Lightning 原生的 LLM 工具包"},{"id":"mamba线性复杂度的状态空间模型","depth":2,"text":"Mamba：线性复杂度的状态空间模型"},{"id":"nanogpt极简-gpt-教学实现","depth":2,"text":"NanoGPT：极简 GPT 教学实现"},{"id":"rwkvrnn-与-transformer-的混合架构","depth":2,"text":"RWKV：RNN 与 Transformer 的混合架构"},{"id":"torchtitanpytorch-原生大规模训练框架","depth":2,"text":"TorchTitan：PyTorch 原生大规模训练框架"},{"id":"jepa非生成式自监督学习架构","depth":2,"text":"JEPA：非生成式自监督学习架构"},{"id":"空间智能理解三维世界的新一代-ai","depth":2,"text":"空间智能：理解三维世界的新一代 AI"},{"id":"transformer-基础架构","depth":2,"text":"Transformer 基础架构"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:foundations:architectures.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/foundations/architectures.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/foundations/architectures","_extension":"md"}